Class SimpleMarkerSymbol

java.lang.Object
  com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.symbols.AbstractSymbol
      com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.symbols.AbstractMarkerSymbol
          com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.core.symbols.SimpleMarkerSymbol
All Implemented Interfaces:
CartographicSupport, IPrintable, IMarkerSymbol, ISymbol, IPersistence
public class SimpleMarkerSymbol
extends AbstractMarkerSymbol

SimpleMarkerSymbol is the most basic symbol for the representation of point objects which can define its size and color apart from the rotation and the offset from a point in the map.

Author:
jaume dominguez faus - jaume.dominguez@iver.es
